            <title>[LU-16883] Update SUSE 15 sp4/sp5 and RHEL 9.0 for LU-15404 fix</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16883</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update SUSE 15 sp4/sp5 for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15404&quot; title=&quot;kernel panic and filesystem corruption in setxattr due to journal transaction restart&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15404&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15404&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similar to RHEL9.1+ there is a trivial conflict when applying ext4-delayed-iput.patch.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately the surrounding context also differs from RHEL9.1+ so SUSE needs it&apos;s own variation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
